description:
In this worship song, we aim to glorify God by singing His praises long into the night. Whether you're a solo singer or part of a worship band, this song is perfect for any worship service.

If you're looking for a low key, relaxing worship song, then this is the song for you! The longer I serve Him, the more I realise how blessed I am to serve Him. Listen and enjoy as we sing His praises long into the night!

Musc performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube Channel
